    "summary": "Hi, I am Marcelo! I am an 8-year experienced journalist and media professional. Currently, I am a freelance correspondent in Europe: bylines in TV Globo and Globo News (Brazil). I am in charge of multiple tasks to bring relevant stories from The Netherlands and the EU to people's televisions back in Brazil. It includes on-field writing and filming; voiceover recording; and interview conduction. I am skilled at writing, verbal communication, content production management, and audiovisual filming, with an academic background in Communications (Brazil). Recently, I have finished my Master in Media and Politics at the University of Amsterdam. During my academic period, I also developed research skills and experience working in international teams.\n\nI am passionate about telling stories of any kind: from relevant human rights initiatives to carnival festivities' love stories. I am also very interested in politics, international relations, sports, travelling, media relations and media advisory. \n\nFeel free to drop me a message if you wish to discuss something!",
